msgctxt "sn48.21:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.21:0.2"
msgid "3. Chaḷindriyavagga "
msgstr "3. The Six Faculties "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 21. Punabbhavasutta → nabbhavo or ñāṇavā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Punabbhavasutta "
msgstr "21. Future Lives "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.204, sc1
msgctxt "sn48.21:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.21:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn48.21:1.3"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ. "
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

#. VAR: Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ → yāvakīvāhaṃ (bj)
#. VAR: abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ → abhisambuddho paccaññāsiṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn48.21:1.4"
msgid "Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nābbhaññāsiṃ, neva tāvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "As long as I didn’t truly understand these five faculties’ gratification, drawback, and escape for what they are, I didn’t announce my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.21:1.5"
msgid "Yato ca khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, athāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya ‘anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
msgstr "But when I did truly understand these five faculties’ gratification, drawback, and escape for what they are, I announced my supreme perfect awakening in this world with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.21:1.6"
msgid "Ñāṇañca pana me dassanaṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "Knowledge and vision arose in me: "

#. VAR: vimutti → cetovimutti (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn48.21:1.7"
msgid "‘akuppā me vimutti, ayamantimā jāti, natthi dāni punabbhavo’”ti. "
msgstr "‘My freedom is unshakable; this is my last rebirth; now there are no more future lives.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.21:1.8"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

